{"id":1158749535,"question_id":3312,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"4 months, 4 weeks","timestamp":1706409298,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"1 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1158749535/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Number of Changing Keys","memory":"42.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int countKeyChanges(String s) {\n        int count = 0;\n        char ch = s.charAt(0);\n        \n        for(int i=1;i<s.length();i++){\n            char c = s.charAt(i);\n            if(c == ch || c+32==ch || c-32 == ch)\n                continue;\n            else{\n                ch = c;\n                count++;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return count;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"number-of-changing-keys","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
